{"tid":945580,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今年巴塞羅那，歐聯真係贏鳩硬啦。","createTime":"2018-12-18T04:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T01:36:55.000Z","uid":43785,"like":34,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2740ce0bd2406f655710868d23b18a9d24352df7","tid":945580,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:08:45.000Z","msg":"今年巴塞羅那，歐聯真係贏鳩硬啦。<br />\n<br />\n今年巴塞羅那條線靚到仆街， <br />\n你依家美斯狀態唔洗問都知輕鬆戰勝里昂。<br />\n<br />\n跟住對曼城利物浦果D英超球隊易過借火。<br />\n拜仁今年又唔撚掂， <br />\n最難咪又係嗰隊巴黎聖日耳門。可惜皇牌之一既尼馬都係跟佢玩鞋炸。<br />\n<br />\n三連霸既皇馬，今年我怕佢年曼聯都贏唔到。<br />\n祖雲達斯唔使講啦，對曼聯同垃圾年青人都贏唔到。廢過英超下游隊。<br />\n<br />\n合曬天時地利人和，今年巴塞那奪歐聯，簡直天命所歸。前中後場冇得输。"},{"pid":"0f1bbfd15825b60da9787314ea44543df1d4b26e","tid":945580,"uid":45498,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:11:03.000Z","msg":"當年宇智波斑出場都係贏硬，<br />\n結果呀絕一刀秒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n火影世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f134134769bcecaed62944bb1ac68ef486251e","tid":945580,"uid":141543,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:11:47.000Z","msg":"小花條友未開季都出到聲今年要拎歐聯，知唔知點解？<br />\n<br />\n因為佢見牙朗離開左皇馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c97041b918aa3049444f652f34991280f9895d2","tid":945580,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4f134134769bcecaed62944bb1ac68ef486251e","tid":945580,"uid":141543,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:11:47.000Z","msg":"小花條友未開季都出到聲今年要拎歐聯，知唔知點解？<br />\n<br />\n因為佢見牙朗離開左皇馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:22:01.000Z","msg":"係佢攞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f6be2026a39f8e2dc31edf7341e358724a47d1","tid":945580,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f1bbfd15825b60da9787314ea44543df1d4b26e","tid